<div id="intro">
        
Darcs is a free and open source, cross-platform version control system,
like <a href="http://git-scm.com/">git</a>, <a
href="http://mercurial.selenic.com/">mercurial</a> or <a
href="http://subversion.apache.org/">svn</a> but with a
very different approach: focus on changes rather
than snapshots. Darcs offers a **freer** way of working, and a
**simpler** user interface. Darcs *does not require a central
server*, and work perfectly in **offline** mode.
        
